<!-- About Project -->

<section class="py-5">

<div class="container">

<div class="card border-0 shadow rounded-4">

<div class="card-body p-5">

<h2 class="fw-bold border-start border-5 border-warning ps-3">
About The Project
</h2>


<p class="text-muted fs-5 mt-4">
Blogify is a full-stack web application developed to provide a platform
for developers to write and share technical blogs. The application focuses
on secure authentication, content management, image uploading, and user
interaction.
</p>


<p class="text-muted fs-5">
The project demonstrates backend development concepts including
Express.js routing, MongoDB database operations, JWT authentication,
password hashing, authorization, and file handling using Multer.
</p>


</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>




