About The Developer
</h2>


<h3 class="fw-bold mt-4">
Syed Fayzan
</h3>


<p class="text-muted fs-5">
Computer Science Engineering student passionate about Full Stack Web
Development and Backend Engineering. Interested in building scalable,
secure, and user-friendly applications using modern technologies.
</p>


<p class="text-muted fs-5">
Blogify was developed to strengthen practical knowledge in backend
development, database management, authentication systems, and real-world
application architecture.
</p>


